description: Kayleigh McEnany hailed the president’s “unprecedented” handling of the crisis. People on Twitter agreed, but not for the reason she wanted.
title: Trump Press Secretary Praises Coronavirus Pandemic Response In The Most Awkward Way
title_page: Trump Press Secretary Praises Coronavirus Pandemic Response In The Most Awkward Way | HuffPost
maintext:
You can't have it both ways. Lying and misinforming the public when Trump speaks and contradicts his health experts.
Oh wait, that's exactly what he's been doing for the past three months. Lying to the nation as the body count soars.
62,000+ Americans are dead thanks to Trump.
